&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;newpage&quot; href=&quot;http://www.treehugger.com/eco-friendly-furniture/sketchchair-open-source-project-lets-you-design-your-own-furniture.html&quot;&gt;http://www.treehugger.com/eco-friendly-furniture/sketchchair-open-source-project-lets-you-design-your-own-furniture.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

